		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 15 Jul 2023 12:04:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[哪几种]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[常吃]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[水果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=4926</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[俗话说“夏吃瓜、秋吃果” 夏季的时候养生常吃 黄瓜、苦瓜等清热降火的瓜类 但是进入秋季之后，秋瓜坏肚 秋季作为 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">俗话说“夏吃瓜、秋吃果”</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">夏季的时候养生常吃</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">黄瓜、苦瓜等清热降火的瓜类</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/09a8a8e4a3c69c201f1da4bec7003387.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">但是进入秋季之后，秋瓜坏肚</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">秋季作为丰收的季节</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不少新鲜水果正大量上市！</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8479810a21544185555cdf580645ac03.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">润肺止咳</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">秋主肺，白色入肺</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">中医讲，梨入心、肺二经</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">《纲目》：润肺凉心，消痰降火</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/ce4b80d2fe60cf9bcf95e6b8dbaa294b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨含有丰富的维生素A、维生素C、维生素E，钾、钙、镁等营养元素。梨富含膳食纤维，对于肠胃来所，是很好的“清洁工”。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/61976457199200cf5c74aaaa54f92125.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨的种类也很繁多</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">香梨多汁、口感甘甜</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">皇冠梨口感更脆，梨香味较浓</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">鸭梨有颗粒感，较甜</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">南果梨口感绵软，适合老年人吃</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">雪花梨的含糖量和含水量高，适合入菜</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">皮梨口感绵软，营养丰富</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">酥梨口感酥脆</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/334af0e380dd4a48752d7595d6e00e63.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">养生厨房的专家和大厨用雪花梨</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">自制了一罐润秋燥的秋梨膏</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/fbf9628a140ca8f6d041b7876823c524.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">秋梨膏</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨 萝卜 藕 冰糖 生姜 大枣 薄荷</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1、雪花梨削皮切成条，放入砂锅中，倒入等量的水、适量大枣、冰糖、姜丝、藕片、萝卜丝，小火熬1小时。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d0ffb27e6b1608ea9c3ffc10c14d5e2f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、用纱布去渣取汁，将汁水放入锅中大火熬，需要不停搅拌，大约1个半小时，呈拉丝状，熬制出膏即可。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">“全科医生”</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果被称为“全科医生”。食品营养科学博士范志红范老师介绍：苹果富含蛋白质、膳食纤维、维生素A、维生素C、维生素E、胡萝卜素等营养元素。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d57d98ef00635b026c694b5a3cad986f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果中富含花青素、多酚、黄酮类物质等抗氧化剂，有助于保护心血管健康。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/773b8e5aa509d0cc0821f76242510584.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果和梨搭配</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">还可以做一碗苹果小吊梨汤</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果小吊梨汤</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果、雪花梨、银耳、大枣</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/af25e7fe9ce079d6a99e667222580102.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">步骤：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1、银耳事先煮制30分钟，银耳与水的比例为1:7.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、雪花梨、苹果、大枣切块，和银耳一起放入电压力锅中。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3、调入少许盐解腻中和，盖盖煮制1小时即可食用。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/5dce41a72f7235044543bf5277c20e2c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨子有降火、润肺、化痰、止咳功效；</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">银耳富含银耳多糖。滋阴润肺，增强人体免疫能力；</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">苹果做熟后可以软化纤维，对胃肠道刺激更小。酚类物质还会增多，有利于保护心脑血管、降脂降压。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">葡萄</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">护血管控血压</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">《随息居饮食谱》中记载葡萄：&#8221;补气，滋肾液，益肝阴，强筋骨，止渴。&#8221;</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a4cf695f861ea2623ba479209715961e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">葡萄中含有白藜芦醇、花青素、花色苷、黄酮类等抗氧化物质，有助于保护血管。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/33f4856c662e4d81ad7e20343a890a24.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">国家级名老中医李乾构李老在养生堂节目上讲解过：葡萄干富含钾元素，常吃还能起到降血压的功效。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">葡萄干能降压、补益气血、滋补肝肾、利小便</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">天麻可以降压祛风、安神、治头晕</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">枸杞子有滋补肝肾的作用</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">三个有降压作用的食材一起泡酒</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">对肝肾阴虚引起的高血压有很好的功效</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/cc7166dc19a2d340b90c91e5c8a909db.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">国家名老中医李乾构降压酒</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/4b2a9b1719b0025096799db477f0a59c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：葡萄干100克、枸杞子60克、天麻30克、黄酒1000毫升。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">吃法：食材放入坛中，浸泡1个月后即可，每晚睡前喝30毫升。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/0e4954cd0d3d8893a25834c2ff4bddb0.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">注意：脾胃实热、血脂高的人群不适合用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">保护视力</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">说完葡萄，来说说它的好姐妹蓝莓</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓被誉为“浆果之王”</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">含有丰富的果胶、SOD、黄酮等物质</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓中的花青素</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">可促进视网膜细胞中视紫质的再生成</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">保护视力、抗衰老、增强免疫力</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/46b6cdda4edbfab59ffc3413e09792f8.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">85岁的国家级名老中医高忠英高老</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">对养生很有一套</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">高老带来2个水果，其中一个就是蓝莓</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/654e712c58f3a6f0b9b02fae4407ba5d.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">高老有一道喜欢吃的美食：蓝莓蒸山药</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓蒸山药</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓洗净放入碗中，在微波炉中打1~2分钟，碾碎就成了蓝莓酱，淋在蒸好的山药上就可以了。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/99d94f2f33bb5ae6bafb820634165944.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蓝莓味酸可以养津液</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">山药既能健脾胃又能滋养肺阴</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">正适合立秋后食用，养好肺脏</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/4089d3390b83263993c91d08b6415226.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">无花果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">清肺 润肠通便</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">除了蓝莓</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">高老带来的另一个水果就是无花果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">无花果富含膳食纤维、维生素、氨基酸</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">有助于润肠通便</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">无花果含有多糖，能起到抗衰老的作用</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/46d72666b79daeb3ff853ce4e8390e5a.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">每天晚饭后，高老的爱人都会给高老用无花果和百合煮水喝，不仅助消化、提高免疫力，还能帮助睡眠。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/6980e7263d5341cfc618c06680893469.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">无花果百合饮</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">鲜百合1整颗、干无花果12个（2个人的量，1人可以减半）</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/cc989794a10f03b234b4d7321686618f.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">用法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">鲜百合清洗干净，去掉黑色的部分，和干的无花果一起放入养生壶中煮15分钟即可饮用，喝完还可以把百合和无花果都吃掉。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/2cb2aaada2dc9dc2fc7a5a5d7fc61520.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">无花果清肺润肺、帮助消化</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">百合清肺润肺、清心安眠</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d8cb6bd68f196f010dca9fcfbfc94e29.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">石榴</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">美容养颜</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">石榴性温、味甘、酸，有生津止渴、滋胃阴、收敛固涩的作用。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/51f5bb43b92f51a9974492e15c07861b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">石榴中维生素C含量9mg/100g</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">维生素E含量4.91mg/100g</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">比苹果还高了2倍多！</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">膳食纤维、视黄醇、钙、镁等矿物质元素</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">钾含量高达231毫克/100克</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">钠含量只有0.9毫克/100克</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/46ba87cf531b252b76069f29537b8b40.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">红石榴中富含矿物质，并具有两大抗氧化成份——红石榴多酚和花青素，可以起到美容肌肤的作用。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f633dc9c62508e39911bbd6ed583556f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">石榴营养美味，但吃起来不方便</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">养生厨房带来快速剥石榴、取汁的方式</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">快速三步：剥石榴+取汁</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">第一步：先取盖，再沿着石榴纹路切开，揪掉石榴中间的膜；</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d851a815b80f606e94c99976b07c4c17.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">第二步：用勺子将石榴拍松散，取出石榴籽；</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/0a1328b65fd533f2eb2376d6ee8ccf25.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">第三步：将石榴籽装进干净的密封袋中，按揉碾压，再切掉袋子的一个角，挤出石榴汁即可。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/05d32202edb95d3cbd310850a3127a38.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">酥肉蒸碗</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">通脊肉、石榴、面粉、淀粉、鸡蛋</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">通脊肉每面切入三分之一，再切成条，加入盐、料酒、胡椒粉、白糖、小苏打抓揉，接着放入一勺面粉、一勺淀粉、鸡蛋清和油均匀挂糊。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">锅中热油，煎制酥肉至双面金黄。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">锅中用葱姜花椒爆锅，放入酱油再加入石榴汁，用蚝油、胡椒粉、盐调味后勾芡。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f0bf59eda3bd01a3bdabfb15adfa5dfb.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">煮好的汁淋在酥肉上蒸20分钟即可。</p><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/3d930854b91238d2878d4ccca8161839.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
